data.description: . Single story 2 bed/2 bath or turn the office into a 3rd bedroom. Oversized lot in the Hill County Retreat @ Alamo Ranch. Community for residents age 55+. Spacious open living room w tray celings for more volume. The kitchen offers SS appliances, gas cooking, breakfast bar, and eat-in dining. Primary bedroom features an ensuite with "Black-Out Blinds" and an oversized double vanity, and a large shower. Nicely-sized secondary bedroom + home office (optional flex room) and guest bath. Tile flooring and plantation shutters throughout. Relax under the shade of the large pergola-covered patio with views of the beautiful landscaping. Convenient to local shopping, dining, movie theater. The community resort offers over 80 clubs to join ranging from Art Group, Dance Group, Theater Club, Wine Group, and many more.   The resort also boasts of Indoor/Outdoor pools (3), 2 hot tubs, Pickleball, Boccee ball & Tennis Courts.  Along with a state of the art fitness center, indoor walking track and miles and miles of outdoor walking trails. There is something for everyone.
